<h1 id="toc1"><span>About Mr. Welsch</span></h1>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:larger;"><strong>Description:</strong></span><br />
Mr. Welsch is the brother of Foundation researcher Dr. Welsch.</p>
<p>No one’s really sure how he began working for the Foundation, but he’s kinda helpful with cleaning and writing stuff up and shit, so nobody really brings it up.</p>
<p>He thinks of Dr. Cardinal as his best friend. He likes to write little stories full of false facts and stick them in with Dr. Cardinal’s paperwork to fuck with him. It’s pretty funny how angry he gets.</p>
<p>Mr. Welsch is often referred to by the nickname ‘OverThinking,’ based on a comment made to him by his driving instructor.</p>
<p><span style="font-size:larger;"><strong>What others have to say about Mr. Welsch:</strong></span></p>
<p><em>&quot;He’s pretty chill.&quot;</em> –Dr. ██████</p>
<p><em>&quot;I mean, I don’t</em> mind <em>him being here.&quot;</em> –Dr. Cardinal</p>
<p><em>&quot;Is he gay? I think he's gay.&quot;</em> –Dr. █████</p>
<p><em>&quot;He's an uppity little shit is what he is.&quot;</em> –Dr. Welsch</p>
<p><em>&quot;Who?&quot;</em> –Dr. ███</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<p>Okey-dokey, that's enough of the semi-in-universe stuff. I'll keep the format, but leave out the lolFoundation.</p>
